This directory is derivative work built on GSM8K
(https://github.com/openai/grade-school-math), MIT-licensed by OpenAI (2021).
The 50 source problems and their canonical numeric answers are taken directly
from GSM8K; `gsm8k_split` and `gsm8k_line_index` in `answers.json` identify
the originating GSM8K record for each item.

Two licenses therefore apply:

(1) Content taken from GSM8K (the source-problem text wherever it appears,
    and the numeric answer in `answers.json`) remains under the **MIT License**
    (Copyright (c) 2021 OpenAI), reproduced below.

(2) Everything else added by Megagon Labs is licensed under the **BSD 3-Clause
    License** (Copyright (c) 2025-2026, Megagon Labs), reproduced below.


